---
import UseCase from '../../../UseCase.astro';
import UseCaseInteractive from '../../../UseCaseInteractive.astro';
import Usage from '../../../Usage.astro';
import UsageItem from '../../../UsageItem.astro';
import Markdown from '../../../Markdown.astro';
import AIBalloon from '../../AIBalloon.astro';
import AIBalloonMessage from '../../AIBalloonMessage.astro';
import AIResponseFollowUp from '../../AIResponseFollowUp.astro';
import AIResponseFollowUpAction from '../../AIResponseFollowUpAction.astro';
import AIResponseMessage from '../../AIResponseMessage.astro';
import HighlightBox from '../../HighlightBox.astro';
---

<UseCase
  title="Avoid Overpromising in Language and Branding"
  description="Use accurate, restrained language in product copy and branding—no 'always accurate', 'fully automated', or 'replaces human judgment' when the system has limits or requires human oversight."
>
  <UseCaseInteractive clsHeight={496} label="Language and branding" toggle>
    <div class="grid gap-600 w-full max-w-9600">
      <AIBalloon>
        <AIBalloonMessage>
          I want to plant 50 creeping rosemary plants along the edge of my garden, which borders a
          slope. Can you give me a complete plan I can directly follow?
        </AIBalloonMessage>
      </AIBalloon>
      <AIResponseMessage>
        <Markdown
          typography="detail"
          content={`
Our tool can help you plan the spacing, estimate how many plants you’ll need, and suggest general planting guidelines for creeping rosemary in a Mediterranean environment.
`}
        />
        <HighlightBox label="Evidence of the challenge" variant="success">
          <Markdown
            typography="detail"
            content={`
However, a slope introduces variables like soil stability, drainage, and erosion risk that require on-site assessment.
`}
          />
        </HighlightBox>
        <HighlightBox label="suggesting a validation phase" variant="success" delay="1">
          <Markdown
            typography="detail"
            content={`
The plan we generate should be used as a guideline, and it’s recommended to validate it with a landscaper or agronomist before planting—especially to ensure the slope remains stable over time.
`}
          />
        </HighlightBox>
      </AIResponseMessage>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-600 w-full max-w-9600">
      <AIBalloon>
        <AIBalloonMessage>
          I want to plant 50 creeping rosemary plants along the edge of my garden, which borders a
          slope. Can you give me a complete plan I can directly follow?
        </AIBalloonMessage>
      </AIBalloon>
      <AIResponseMessage>
        <HighlightBox label="False total reliability promise" variant="error">
          <Markdown
            typography="detail"
            content={`
Yes, our AI can generate a fully reliable, ready-to-execute planting plan for your slope. Just follow the spacing and instructions provided, and the rosemary will stabilize the edge without any additional work or expert input.
`}
          />
        </HighlightBox>
      </AIResponseMessage>
    </div>
  </UseCaseInteractive>
  <Usage>
    <UsageItem variant="do">
      Use language that reflects real capabilities: assist, suggest, draft, help—and that the user
      reviews or decides.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="dont">
      Claim always-accurate, fully automated, or no-review-needed when the system has limits or
      requires human oversight.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="do">
      Align marketing and in-product copy with what the AI actually does and doesn't do.
    </UsageItem>
    <UsageItem variant="dont">
      Let branding promise more than the product delivers; avoid "replaces human judgment" or
      similar overclaims.
    </UsageItem>
  </Usage>
</UseCase>
